{"tid":575853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【銀行械劫】行劫東亞銀行總行持槍男   天水圍落網","createTime":"2018-02-28T12:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T10:40:58.000Z","uid":48093,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2c80a1d60d25c691cc1186c935266c69968fe3","tid":575853,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180228/large/1519805738_8682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180228%2Flarge%2F1519805738_8682.jpg&h=5c211f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180228/large/1519804491_447e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180228%2Flarge%2F1519804491_447e.jpg&h=38234336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180228/large/1519804493_34bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180228%2Flarge%2F1519804493_34bc.jpg&h=8feeee40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【20:28】消息稱，持槍賊人在天水圍區落網<br />\n【19:55】警方仍然封鎖銀行現場調查<br />\n【18:05】東亞銀行主席兼行政總裁李國寶於劫案發生後約1小時，即下午4時許離開總行<br />\n【18:05】東亞銀行發言人表示，證實今午有一賊人到總行行劫，銀行職員已即時報警處理，事件中未有客戶和職員受傷，損失金額則為數萬元。<br />\n【18:00】大批警員於東亞總行調查<br />\n【17:30】新增劫案過程片段，可見賊人持槍指嚇櫃台職員<br />\n【15:55】受事故影響，中環站列車服務受阻<br />\n<br />\n中環德輔道中10號東亞銀行，發生懷疑持槍劫案。下午3時半左右，一名中年男子，持槍指向櫃台搶劫，掠去約7萬元款項後即奪門逃去。警方接報後，派出大批警員荷槍實彈到場搜捕，更一度於中環站月台戒備，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n從現場閉路電視所見，匪徒年約50歲，穿黑色長袖衫，沒有蒙面，並且雙手緊握曲尺手槍，槍頭指向兩名櫃台職員。只見職員將現鈔放入賊人帶來的膠袋，賊人得手後逃去，為時僅16秒。"},{"pid":"1e39f0f185ea9db61e3c30d4cadfc194fd6145b8","tid":575853,"uid":60831,"like":132,"dislike":1,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"過咗五粒鐘仲喺天水圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bb73673c3c131e0a1c140c9dcf4ff103f73bd4","tid":575853,"uid":48093,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"係咪應該著草返大陸好D?"},{"pid":"027ff9b4eb36c9f16d3a761985dd717344a165cc","tid":575853,"uid":16676,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"quote":{"pid":"1e39f0f185ea9db61e3c30d4cadfc194fd6145b8","tid":575853,"uid":60831,"like":132,"dislike":1,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"過咗五粒鐘仲喺天水圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:41:09.000Z","msg":"搭車出到中環<br />\n<br />\n拎得幾萬蚊咋<br />\n邊夠著草<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解唔近近地去元朗大馬路果間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53422bcbb6f4b30887e1b9d1d3abf7d407247d0","tid":575853,"uid":102096,"like":10,"dislike":98,"score":-88,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b44032283decb75739610a469ed660c9a45dc590","tid":575853,"uid":16676,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:42:48.000Z","msg":"算醒目, 知道塞車唔搭巴士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐東涌線過海再轉西鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd661bd9af8144d2a6799f3a8994fc8e9bd3a9d5","tid":575853,"uid":93649,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:43:14.000Z","msg":"5個鐘夠佢call幾隻靚G"},{"pid":"bec02f73cbaa2aab684a1a272a1dfab32f6543c3","tid":575853,"uid":54431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e9bb73673c3c131e0a1c140c9dcf4ff103f73bd4","tid":575853,"uid":48093,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"係咪應該著草返大陸好D?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"七萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c50f0ab294349727661fa1bff099e6daa28